desc: The RoundedRectangle element is used to draw a rounded rectangle.

x.desc: The vertical position of the rounded rectangle.

y.desc: The horizontal position of the rounded rectangle.

width.desc: The width of the rounded rectangle.

height.desc: The height of the rounded rectangle.

ellipseWidth.desc: The ellipse width of the rounded rectangle.

ellipseHeight.desc: The ellipse height of the rounded rectangle.
